## Draft expanded use-case description

**Use Case:** Draft

**Actors:** User 1, User 2, System

**Description:** Each user enters a team name and is them prompted to ready up. Once each player has chose to ready up the system begins the draft. The system will randomize the draft order then that user begins drafting. Each player can view all the available players and once a selection is made the system will remove that player from the list. Once each user has a full team the system will end the draft.

**Cross Ref:** Requirements R1, R2, R3, R4, R5, R6

